{
  "texts": [
    "The catalog is based on the same LAMOST-MRS data release (DR10 v1.0) as used in this work.",
    "Although the work of Liu et al (2024) is intended for the compact object candidates in binaries, the criterion adopted by the work (large or rapid radial-velocity variation) guarantees a reliable catalog from the perspective of close binaries.",
    "We cross-match our sample (after the above screening conditions) with the catalog of Liu et al (2024) and find that six stellar sources are in common.",
    "These common objects are removed from our sample.",
    "There are 2,148,470 spectral records and 1,019,861 stellar sources in the original LAMOST MRS Parameter Catalog used in this work."
  ]
}